<SysML:Block id="329bc57c-f96b-11f0-9b62-1063c8f53908">
<name>
<val>Gearbox</val>
</name>
<nestingClass>
<ref refid="ad8b2d96-f96c-11f0-ada4-1063c8f53908"/>
</nestingClass>
<note>
<val>A geared mechanism to aplify the servo rotational moment and to be able torotate the motor, while simultaniously holding it stable.

As most servos have a 300deg rotation a 3:1 gearing ratio should be fine</val>
</note>
